Networking momentum fades quickly if action is delayed. After an event, prospects meet multiple professionals, and timely communication helps you stand out. The 48-hour follow-up rule exists because speed builds trust and professionalism.
However, relying on manual processes slows everything down. A reliable Business card scanner app ensures contacts are digitized instantly, reducing errors and administrative delays. With organized digital records, you can send personalized emails, schedule meetings, and continue conversations while they are still fresh. Faster follow-ups translate into stronger relationships and higher conversion potential.
